
===================================
📌 1. Finglish Version (Persian Latin Script)
===================================

📖 **Tashrih:**
    Dastoor `gstreamer-codec-install` baraye nasb codec-haye ghesmate GStreamer estefade mishavad. In dastoor komak mikonad ta shoma betavanid file-haye multimedia-ye mokhtalef ra ba estefade az GStreamer pakhsh konid. Agar GStreamer codec-i ke lazem ast ra nadashte bashad, in dastoor be shoma dar nasb an codec komak mikonad.

⚙️ **Gozine-ha:**
    🔹 `gstreamer-codec-install`  --> 🚀 Shoru kardane nasb codec-ha-ye gomshode.
    🔹 `gstreamer-codec-install VIDEOTYPE` --> 🎞️ Nasbe codec baraye no'e makhsose video (masalan: AVI, MKV).
    🔹 `gstreamer-codec-install AUDIOTYPE` --> 🎵 Nasbe codec baraye no'e makhsose audio (masalan: MP3, AAC).

🛠 **Mesal-ha:**

    $ gstreamer-codec-install

    🔹 Shoru kardane dastoor baraye nasb codec-ha-ye gomshode-ye GStreamer.

    $ gstreamer-codec-install AVI

    🔹 Nasb codec baraye file-haye video-ye AVI.

✅ **Mesal sade:**

    $ gstreamer-codec-install MP3

    🔹 In dastoor codec-haye lazem baraye pakhsh file-haye MP3 ra nasb mikonad. Agar dastoor codec-i ra peyda konad ke nasb nist, az shoma khohahad ke an ra nasb konid.

===================================
📌 2. English Version
===================================

📖 **Description:**
    The `gstreamer-codec-install` command is used to install missing codecs for the GStreamer multimedia framework. This command helps you to play various multimedia files using GStreamer. If GStreamer lacks a required codec, this command assists you in installing it.

⚙️ **Options:**
    🔹 `gstreamer-codec-install`  --> 🚀 Start the installation of missing codecs.
    🔹 `gstreamer-codec-install VIDEOTYPE` --> 🎞️ Install codec for a specific video type (e.g., AVI, MKV).
    🔹 `gstreamer-codec-install AUDIOTYPE` --> 🎵 Install codec for a specific audio type (e.g., MP3, AAC).

🛠 **Examples:**

    $ gstreamer-codec-install

    🔹 Starts the command to install missing GStreamer codecs.

    $ gstreamer-codec-install AVI

    🔹 Installs codecs for AVI video files.

✅ **Simple Example:**

    $ gstreamer-codec-install MP3

    🔹 This command installs the necessary codecs to play MP3 files. If the command finds a codec that is not installed, it will prompt you to install it.
